Smash Garlic
Slice Peppers
Shred Cheese
Slice Pork
Cut Kimchi
Marinate Pork & Peppers in
    Mirin
    Soy
    Sesame Oil
    Garlic

Boil Anchovy Kelp Broth
Set Aside
Brown Kimchi in Sesame Oil
Add Broth
Simmer for 40min-1hr
Set Aside
Take out Pizza Dough
Turn on oven
Chop Kimchi
Shape Pizza Dough
Top Pizza
Bake